('54032','19104','5','Comfortable country hotel for sale'),
('54033','19105','5','This stately manor dated from the 16th century is surrounded by a Mediterranean garden, a rich variety of almond, orange, lemon and fig trees and ample fields of grain. Nestled in romantic hills, it is only a 7 minutes drive away from the sea with its beautiful beaches.\r\nIn July 1999 (after extensive restoration) it was converted into an elegant country hotel, that satisfies the highest demands. It is decorated with tastefully selected artwork and antiques, which provide comfort and a beautiful, authentic atmosphere. A perfect place for letting go and unwinding.\r\nFive different golf courses will be reached within 15-25 minutes by car, and another golf course will be built just a 5 minutes drive away.\r\nThe property is set on plot of 57,000 m² with a living area of 1,600 m² and has an own water supply well plus a water deposit. Electricity and telephone connections are installed.\r\nThere are 9 double rooms, 2 junior suites (one with roof terrace), 3 suites (one with roof terrace), 1 apartment (54 m² including a kitchenette), all equipped with en suite bathroom, ISDN telephone line for internet, satellite TV connection, minibar, safe, air conditioning h / c, etc.\r\nThe extension of two further double room is easy. Moreover, there is the possibility to create 3 double rooms by reconstructing a ruin. The hotel has reception, lobby, fireplace, bar, lounge, library, restaurant with professional kitchen, various storage rooms and walk-in refrigerator / freezing rooms and a fitness room with massage area and sauna with solarium.\r\nA large, well-maintained park-like garden with automatic irrigation, wide outdoor lighting, a horse stable with 6 boxes/stalls including water and light, a large pool and a tennis court complete this offer.\r\nAs the hotel is still in operation and for discretionary purposes, we are not able to publish any photos and location details. Please contact our office for further information.'),
